This paper is about Natural Language Processing (NLP) and machine comprehension of reading passages and questions. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves the use of machine learning models, which suggests the sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with information retrieval, which is related to the sub-category cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves the use of attention mechanisms, which is related to the sub-category cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
